WEBVTT

1
00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:23.395
NONG PRADU VILLAGE.
NORTHEAST THAILAND

2
00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:23.791
Down!

3
00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:43.758
Quick! Quick!

4
00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:53.391
Up! Up!

5
00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:55.155
Quick!

6
00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:57.191
Quick! Quick!

7
00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:07.398
Hurry! Hurry!

8
00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:09.238
Keep going!

9
00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:13.677
Quick! Quick!

10
00:03:32.920 --> 00:03:34.797
Follow him! Quick!

11
00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:37.309
After him! Quick!

12
00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:50.352
Quick! Now!

13
00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:52.792
Quick! Quick!

14
00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:00.392
Quick! Quick!

15
00:04:00.520 --> 00:04:02.351
Down! Go down!

16
00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:07.318
Here he comes.

17
00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:21.348
Catch him!

18
00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:30.558
God bless him.

19
00:04:31.920 --> 00:04:33.672
Quiet. please!

20
00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:39.079
The winner this year is... young Ting!

21
00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:52.798
Welcome. people of Nong Pradu.

22
00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:54.956
Welcome. all who came

23
00:04:55.080 --> 00:04:59.790
for the presentation of robes
to our revered Ong-Bak.

24
00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:03.276
which is our mind and soul.

25
00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:08.235
This ceremony is a prelude
to the great festival of Ong-Bak

26
00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:11.033
that will commence here in seven days.

27
00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:13.879
And it will be an important ceremony.

28
00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:20.473
which is held
just once every 24 years.

29
00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:23.637
It marks the auspicious completion
of two cycles.

30
00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:26.877
Prosperity will be in our community.

31
00:05:36.680 --> 00:05:39.148
Where's the Buddha amulet?

32
00:05:42.640 --> 00:05:47.316
It shows signs of wear.
The head's slightly chipped.

33
00:05:47.760 --> 00:05:49.512
Hardly perfect condition.

34
00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:52.473
200.000 baht is a good price.

35
00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.318
Why won't you sell it?

36
00:05:57.720 --> 00:06:00.359
Come on. Name your price.

37
00:06:00.480 --> 00:06:02.550
Don. it's not for sale.

38
00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:08.789
I've come all the way from Bangkok.
I took time off work.

39
00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:12.437
I never told you I'd sell it.

40
00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:15.518
I'm keeping it for my son. Humlae.

41
00:06:15.640 --> 00:06:19.713
for when he is ordained as a monk
for Ong-Bak.

42
00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:24.400
When you decide to sell. call me.

43
00:06:25.160 --> 00:06:28.516
No. No way.
I don't have a telephone.

44
00:06:28.640 --> 00:06:30.551
I'll give you my address.

45
00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:34.434
When you decide to sell.
write me a letter.

46
00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:50.634
Isn't it nice. Grandma? I want
to give it to Ting when he's ordained.

47
00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:52.478
Nice.

48
00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:56.752
He was born during
the Ong-Bak festival. wasn't he?

49
00:06:57.480 --> 00:07:02.554
Well. if you say so.
Ting had an unfortunate start in life.

50
00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:07.076
He was left at a temple
when he was a baby.

51
00:07:07.200 --> 00:07:09.191
A monk happened to see him.

52
00:07:09.320 --> 00:07:13.632
He took pity on him
and looked after him.

53
00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:19.278
Perhaps he is fortunate
and he is protected by Ong-Bak.

54
00:07:26.640 --> 00:07:28.551
Yan Yothee. (Grounded Feet.)

55
00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:30.716
Jarakae Fad Hang. (Crocodile's Kick.)

56
00:07:30.840 --> 00:07:32.990
Pajon Chang San.
(Great Elephant's Power.)

57
00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.633
Hanuman Thawai Waen.
(Great Monkey Offers the Ring.)

58
00:07:34.760 --> 00:07:35.909
Acha Phayong. (Great Horse.)

59
00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:38.873
Khwang Liew Lang. (Great Deer.)
Ongkot Kong Phrakhan. (Giant's Sword.)

60
00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.638
Luang Daen Hera. (Great Invader.)

61
00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:44.196
Yotha Kluen Tap. (Prepare for War.)
Kacha Tokman. (Elephant in Season.)

62
00:07:44.320 --> 00:07:45.992
Hakmum Hewarat. (The Cliff is Crumbled.)

63
00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:47.997
Yat Tiem Fa. (Reach for the Sky.)

64
00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.712
Kwang Sabat Na. (The Deer's Flick.)

65
00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:51.671
Ramasoon Kwang Kwan. (Giant's Axe.)

66
00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:54.394
Kluen Kratop Fang. (Mad Currents.)

67
00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:56.954
Tapien Fang Tor. (Crumbling Block.)

68
00:07:57.080 --> 00:07:59.435
Khun Dap Jap Ling.
(Giant Catching Monkey.)

69
00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:02.120
Hak Kor Erawan.
(Strangling the Great Elephant.)

70
00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:04.674
Ngoo Lai Tokae. (Snake Chasing Gecko.)

71
00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:06.153
Par Satarn. (Earth Moves.)

72
00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:07.918
Nang Miew. (Wild Cat Fight.)

73
00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:10.713
Khon Rook Khamoon. (Great Lance.)
Hak Narok. (Challenge Hell.)

74
00:08:10.840 --> 00:08:12.319
Yod Yotha. (Confront the Enemy.)

75
00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:14.510
Pamai Thang. (Crushing the Teeth.)

76
00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:31.712
I have taught you the art of Muay Thai.
and passed on the knowledge.

77
00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:37.676
Now I ask you never to use it.
Is that clear. Ting?

78
00:08:37.800 --> 00:08:39.677
Yes. Master.

79
00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:41.756
Good.

80
00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:53.548
It's good that you didn't understand.

81
00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:56.148
Am I right?

82
00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:09.559
In his youth. your master learned
the ancient art of Muay Thai

83
00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:12.433
under the great master Kru Dam.

84
00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:17.956
The master. he was impatient
to try out his skills.

85
00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:23.713
In a rope fist fight.
he killed his opponent.

86
00:09:24.680 --> 00:09:29.037
Overcome with guilt.
he decided to become a monk.

87
00:09:29.160 --> 00:09:31.958
Muay Thai is dangerous.

88
00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:38.397
He doesn't want you fooling around
with it. Is it clear now?

89
00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.989
If you're still not convinced...

90
00:09:45.400 --> 00:09:48.153
Come. Fight with me. Ting.

91
00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:51.277
Uncle!

92
00:10:25.760 --> 00:10:28.593
You vandals! What are you doing?

93
00:10:39.560 --> 00:10:40.515
Move it!

94
00:10:51.280 --> 00:10:55.637
That scumbag Don
severed the head of Ong-Bak!

95
00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:03.233
He also stole the poor box. Master.

96
00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:08.872
- Don is such a devil!
- Wicked man.

97
00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:16.075
If we can't recover Ong-Bak's head.
our village is doomed!

98
00:11:17.160 --> 00:11:19.628
Everybody. calm down.

99
00:11:19.760 --> 00:11:27.314
We'll find a way to bring the Buddha's
head back before the great ceremony.

100
00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:30.632
But who will bring it back?

101
00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:35.152
I'll bring it back!

102
00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:39.717
I know where Don lives.

103
00:11:42.520 --> 00:11:47.674
The fate of the whole village
lies in your hands.

104
00:11:48.920 --> 00:11:52.276
This sacred amulet
contains Nilapat herbs.

105
00:11:52.400 --> 00:11:56.871
My grandfather told me
it belonged to Kru Dam.

106
00:11:57.800 --> 00:12:00.917
Keep it close to your heart.

107
00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:07.550
Here's Don's address.

108
00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:12.349
And please give this letter to Humlae.

109
00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:16.270
Ting. be sure to bring Ong-Bak back...

110
00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:20.234
safely home to our village.

111
00:12:28.920 --> 00:12:32.549
Here's some money for food.

112
00:12:33.800 --> 00:12:36.837
All our hopes go with you.

113
00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:41.870
Mother gave me this ring
before she died.

114
00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:46.232
Warn. take care of Grandmother.

115
00:13:04.640 --> 00:13:08.076
Everybody. give what you can.

116
00:13:10.080 --> 00:13:12.640
For the journey.

117
00:13:22.640 --> 00:13:24.790
BANGKOK

118
00:13:48.120 --> 00:13:49.951
Shit. I lost!

119
00:13:59.880 --> 00:14:02.792
Bugger off! Come here!

120
00:14:02.920 --> 00:14:06.629
Who'd you pick to race?
We lost by miles!

121
00:14:06.760 --> 00:14:10.469
What the hell you are talking about?
Win some. lose some!

122
00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:13.478
You're the big boss -
you should be fair.

123
00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:17.593
- You put up a girl against me?
- So I'm a girl. So what?

124
00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:21.156
Do you know who you're talking to?

125
00:14:21.280 --> 00:14:24.158
Shame you don't race
as fast as you talk!

126
00:14:24.280 --> 00:14:25.838
Screw you!

127
00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:44.519
- Hey. why aren't you giving me cash?
- You used speed to bet with.

128
00:14:45.160 --> 00:14:48.630
But you said cash was fine.

129
00:14:50.720 --> 00:14:52.711
OK!

130
00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:03.837
Here's 10.000 baht.
The rest's security on your debts.

131
00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:07.589
I pay you interest every month
and it's not due yet.

132
00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:10.109
Give me some spending money.

133
00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:14.597
- Take it or leave it.
- I guess it's better than nothing.

134
00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:24.551
Hey. give me those.

135
00:15:24.680 --> 00:15:27.877
Fuck's sake! Give them to me.

136
00:15:30.640 --> 00:15:34.679
You got cash.
You can leave me two tabs for my boys.

137
00:15:34.800 --> 00:15:39.555
You guys can score what you need
anytime. anywhere.

138
00:15:39.680 --> 00:15:41.796
Why do you want to take mine?

139
00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:46.118
It's too strong for these pussies.
They might OD. Trust me.

140
00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:48.549
- Give me.
- No!

141
00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:01.429
Shithead!

142
00:16:10.360 --> 00:16:14.069
There you are at last. George.
Quick!

143
00:16:14.200 --> 00:16:17.875
Where's my share?
Quick! I'm in a hurry.

144
00:16:18.000 --> 00:16:23.154
That asshole Peng got wise to our scam.
He kept all the money.

145
00:16:23.280 --> 00:16:27.193
What?
If this is a joke. it's not funny!

146
00:16:27.320 --> 00:16:29.595
Look! Check out my face!

147
00:16:29.720 --> 00:16:32.518
You think I did that to myself.
for Christ's sake?

148
00:16:36.480 --> 00:16:38.835
Hands off! I just got beaten up!

149
00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:41.872
Your bad luck.
How could he tell?

150
00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:44.833
Sod it. Have you got 200 baht?

151
00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:48.316
Hold on! I haven't got my fair share.
Pay up first. borrow later!

152
00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:53.309
Muay. you always take
your share of the dough. every penny.

153
00:16:53.440 --> 00:16:55.670
but never your share of the beatings.

154
00:16:55.800 --> 00:16:59.634
Serves you right. you fool!
Obvious. isn't it?

155
00:16:59.760 --> 00:17:02.752
I messed up. smarty-pants?

156
00:17:02.880 --> 00:17:08.398
Peng has given me three days to pay up
or he'll come after me.

157
00:17:09.040 --> 00:17:11.349
Humlae!

158
00:17:13.760 --> 00:17:17.230
It is you. isn't it?
Greetings!

159
00:17:17.360 --> 00:17:19.635
Muay. is he a friend of yours?

160
00:17:19.760 --> 00:17:23.514
What do you mean?
He's talking to you.

161
00:17:24.040 --> 00:17:26.076
You know this hillbilly?

162
00:17:26.200 --> 00:17:28.873
Don't you remember me?
Ting from Nong Pradu.

163
00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:31.468
Yeah. right! I don't know you.

164
00:17:31.600 --> 00:17:35.479
I don't know you. Got that. sucker?

165
00:17:35.600 --> 00:17:37.750
I remember you. You're Humlae.

166
00:17:37.880 --> 00:17:42.112
What kind of a name is that?
Dumbest name I've ever heard.

167
00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:46.791
- Clear out. before I kick your ass!
- Go easy. Humlae...

168
00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:49.158
Sorry. George. I mean.

169
00:17:49.280 --> 00:17:54.308
You think you know everything?
Go away - as far as you can!

170
00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:58.276
- What was the name of your village?
- Nong Pradu.

171
00:17:58.400 --> 00:18:02.518
Right. Nong Pradu.
I'll go.

172
00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:06.474
I'll leave the Nong Pradu boys to it.
Right?

173
00:18:06.600 --> 00:18:09.319
He shows up and you take off!
Go!

174
00:18:09.440 --> 00:18:13.718
- But leave me some dough.
- Buy yourself some medicine.

175
00:18:13.840 --> 00:18:16.195
See ya. Humlae.

176
00:18:17.800 --> 00:18:22.237
As for you. country boy.
go back where you came from!

177
00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:26.237
Humlae.
your dad gave me a letter for you.

178
00:18:26.360 --> 00:18:28.635
I don't know you. Scram!

179
00:18:34.600 --> 00:18:37.672
This is my room.
Take no notice about earlier.

180
00:18:37.800 --> 00:18:40.678
Close the door.
or it'll be swarming with mosquitoes.

181
00:18:40.800 --> 00:18:44.839
I was out of line.
I was in a bad mood.

182
00:18:45.840 --> 00:18:52.712
Humlae.
our village is in big trouble.

183
00:18:53.600 --> 00:18:56.319
Don and his men stole Ong-Bak's head.

184
00:18:57.400 --> 00:19:03.077
Our headman told me to come
and find you so we could get it back.

185
00:19:04.560 --> 00:19:07.916
- I have Don's address here.
- Save it for later.

186
00:19:08.040 --> 00:19:10.838
Here. dump your gear
and go take a shower. Go on.

187
00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:16.080
Come on. quick! It'll do you good.
Through here.

188
00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:20.034
- Then can we...?
- Later. Here's a towel.

189
00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:22.276
I'll even turn on the light for you.
Go.

190
00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:25.233
Soap's on the left.
toothpaste on the right.

191
00:19:25.360 --> 00:19:28.716
Don't wank. OK?
I don't want you to slip and die.

192
00:19:28.840 --> 00:19:33.470
Hi. is that you. Muay?
Meet me at the Khaosan Road.

193
00:19:33.600 --> 00:19:36.398
Yes. the fight club.

194
00:20:17.320 --> 00:20:20.756
Still time to place a bet on Ali?

195
00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:22.835
Yes.

196
00:20:23.840 --> 00:20:25.398
All of it.

197
00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:40.117
Where's the amulet?

198
00:20:42.080 --> 00:20:44.594
Their pigheaded chief refused to sell.

199
00:20:44.720 --> 00:20:48.349
So I took Ong-Bak's head instead. boss.

200
00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:52.598
He's the village deity. boss.
They revere him.

201
00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:57.795
You wasted your time.

202
00:20:57.920 --> 00:21:00.229
It's a lousy lump of stone.

203
00:21:01.520 --> 00:21:03.670
You're such a jerk!

204
00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:07.355
Get this rock out of my sight...

205
00:21:08.680 --> 00:21:10.671
before I really get mad!

206
00:21:16.920 --> 00:21:19.992
Your boys keep letting you down. huh?

207
00:21:20.120 --> 00:21:27.117
And now Pearl Harbour's going to get
the kamikaze treatment from my boy Ali.

208
00:22:00.920 --> 00:22:04.151
- Haven't got any money yet.
- I'm trying to get it for you.

209
00:22:04.280 --> 00:22:08.637
I don't want your money.
I can find it myself.

210
00:22:08.760 --> 00:22:11.115
Are you pushing drugs these days?

211
00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:13.154
Yes!

212
00:22:17.960 --> 00:22:20.349
You seem very sure of that.

213
00:22:21.440 --> 00:22:24.000
If you think your guy can win.
up the stakes!

214
00:22:24.120 --> 00:22:26.759
Whatever. I have no limit.

215
00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:29.553
Don't argue. You never understand me!

216
00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:34.708
You asshole!
Why do you have to act like this?

217
00:22:34.840 --> 00:22:37.149
Muay. you're not my mother!

218
00:22:37.280 --> 00:22:41.717
It's because you've got no parents
that you're such a loose cannon!

219
00:22:41.840 --> 00:22:45.674
Yes. I'm bad -
but I've looked after you.

220
00:22:45.800 --> 00:22:48.951
From now on. stay away from me.

221
00:22:56.880 --> 00:22:59.394
Just ask whenever you want.

222
00:23:42.320 --> 00:23:46.552
Next fight. if you're still game...

223
00:23:46.680 --> 00:23:49.877
maybe you'd like to up the stakes.

224
00:23:57.200 --> 00:23:58.428
Bastard!

225
00:24:02.040 --> 00:24:03.632
Shit!

226
00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:09.233
- Where's the villagers' money?
- What?

227
00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:12.193
- Where's the money?
- How should I know?

228
00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:15.230
There!

229
00:24:24.120 --> 00:24:27.715
New contender!

230
00:24:29.400 --> 00:24:33.871
Come on. lay your bets!
Three to one. Quick!

231
00:24:37.480 --> 00:24:41.758
Wow! What's country boy
think he's doing?

232
00:24:42.360 --> 00:24:45.033
Yup. we can wave goodbye to Ting.

233
00:24:46.280 --> 00:24:48.396
I'll give you ten to one.

234
00:24:49.400 --> 00:24:52.278
But perhaps you'd better not risk it.

235
00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:55.951
OK. let's up the ante: One million.

236
00:24:57.360 --> 00:24:58.395
I'm in.

237
00:24:58.720 --> 00:25:01.393
I don't want a fight. just my cash.

238
00:25:01.520 --> 00:25:03.875
No sweat. kid. leave it to me.

239
00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:05.228
Fight!

240
00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:33.511
- What's your name. brother?
- Ting. from Nong Pradu village. I'II...

241
00:25:33.640 --> 00:25:36.552
Ting. the Pradu Legend!

242
00:25:49.680 --> 00:25:53.195
No. I just want my money back.

243
00:25:54.800 --> 00:25:56.392
What an idiot!

244
00:26:04.680 --> 00:26:08.673
Hey! Why didn't you take
the dough. lunkhead?

245
00:26:09.480 --> 00:26:14.474
If you want to fight again. let me know.
You're good. you can beat anyone.

246
00:26:14.600 --> 00:26:17.433
I see us getting rich!
Super rich!

247
00:26:17.560 --> 00:26:19.755
I don't fight for money.

248
00:26:19.880 --> 00:26:23.395
What got into you.
stealing the villagers' money?

249
00:26:23.520 --> 00:26:25.351
Not stealing. investing.

250
00:26:25.480 --> 00:26:28.711
When we're rich.
I'll help you find Ong-Bak.

251
00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:32.315
- Really?
- You bet.

252
00:26:34.920 --> 00:26:37.514
Here's Don's address.
Can you take me?

253
00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:40.200
Hold onto it. I'll take you later.

254
00:26:40.320 --> 00:26:42.834
Lend me some now.
I need it.

255
00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:46.157
I'll pay you back when I win.
Then I'll take you anywhere.

256
00:26:46.280 --> 00:26:48.271
I promise. Trust me.

257
00:26:53.200 --> 00:26:57.352
OK. get lost! Shithead!
Stupid country boy!

258
00:26:57.480 --> 00:26:59.232
I was trying to be nice!
Shithead!

259
00:26:59.360 --> 00:27:01.590
If you tell him to sod off.
where's he going to sleep?

260
00:27:01.720 --> 00:27:03.995
Fuck him!
Or do you want him to sleep with you?

261
00:27:04.120 --> 00:27:06.236
You must be joking.

262
00:27:07.360 --> 00:27:10.875
What are we going to do this time?
He'll definitely kill me.

263
00:27:11.000 --> 00:27:14.390
Muay. you flog the speed
at the gambling joint.

264
00:27:14.520 --> 00:27:18.115
We'll split the profit.
We'll get cash. I know the owner well.

265
00:27:18.240 --> 00:27:21.915
You never learn from your mistakes.

266
00:27:22.040 --> 00:27:24.793
I told you I don't want
to get involved with drugs.

267
00:27:24.920 --> 00:27:28.959
Help me. please.
You want me to get beaten up?

268
00:27:29.080 --> 00:27:30.308
Will you help?

269
00:27:30.440 --> 00:27:33.796
All right. but I have to find a good day.
How about tomorrow?

270
00:27:33.920 --> 00:27:36.036
That's what I want. Now I feel good.

271
00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:49.473
No need to look grateful.
I'll take 70. you take 30.

272
00:27:49.600 --> 00:27:52.068
Muay. 50-50!

273
00:27:52.200 --> 00:27:54.236
- 70-30.
- 50-50.

274
00:27:54.360 --> 00:27:55.998
70-30.

275
00:28:27.920 --> 00:28:31.549
"About the loan you asked for
to set up a business in Bangkok -

276
00:28:31.680 --> 00:28:36.595
I can't help you. because
of the severe drought in the village."

277
00:28:36.720 --> 00:28:39.757
"Worse still.
Don stole Ong-Bak's head."

278
00:28:39.880 --> 00:28:45.432
"I want you to help Ting
to get it back to change our fortune."

279
00:28:45.560 --> 00:28:47.630
Numbskulls!

280
00:28:56.120 --> 00:28:58.714
NONG PRADU VILLAGE

281
00:29:15.320 --> 00:29:19.871
Warn. hardly any water is left in the well.
What are we going to do?

282
00:29:24.360 --> 00:29:29.514
God. please help Ting find Ong-Bak.

283
00:29:36.200 --> 00:29:38.316
How's business?

284
00:29:40.560 --> 00:29:43.074
Hey. what's up? Losing?

285
00:29:43.200 --> 00:29:45.839
- Hi. big brother.
- Hi. George.

286
00:29:45.960 --> 00:29:48.190
Where the fuck you been?

287
00:29:48.320 --> 00:29:52.598
- Working with friends.
- I'm short-staffed. Help me. Quick!

288
00:29:52.720 --> 00:29:56.599
- Sorry. I'm busy.
- Don't argue! Now!

289
00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:59.473
- Another time.
- Now! Move it!

290
00:30:00.600 --> 00:30:02.511
Deal.

291
00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:07.434
Get lost. you can't deal.

292
00:30:09.320 --> 00:30:13.916
Old man. bet! At your age.
you should be home looking after kids.

293
00:30:14.040 --> 00:30:16.349
Well. I need pleasure.

294
00:30:17.080 --> 00:30:20.868
- What are you staring at. asshole?
- Go over there!

295
00:30:21.000 --> 00:30:25.312
Time to change the hair colour.
Stop copying my cool image.

296
00:30:29.080 --> 00:30:34.393
Put the money in. Let's see your money.
If you lose. don't kill me.

297
00:30:34.520 --> 00:30:35.839
Don't cheat!

298
00:30:36.560 --> 00:30:38.437
Nine!
Clear winner.

299
00:30:39.800 --> 00:30:44.430
- I lost!
- Deal me in! Quick. Quick.

300
00:30:44.560 --> 00:30:47.757
- Put the money in. Bet now.
- Let me join in.

301
00:30:47.880 --> 00:30:51.634
- You got money?
- 3.000 baht. Enough for you?

302
00:30:51.760 --> 00:30:56.276
Let her play. if she wants to lose.
We'll clean her out like an enema!

303
00:30:56.400 --> 00:30:58.391
- 200.
- 200.

304
00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:02.110
No cheating!

305
00:31:02.960 --> 00:31:06.509
- Double eight!
- Pay up. everybody!

306
00:31:06.640 --> 00:31:08.835
Rake in the dough. George!

307
00:31:08.960 --> 00:31:12.839
Wait. I have double nine. Pay up.

308
00:31:15.040 --> 00:31:18.112
Damn! Here's 400 baht.

309
00:31:18.240 --> 00:31:21.596
- Thanks. big boss.
- Put the money in.

310
00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:27.834
- The house has a six. Shit!
- I have a nine.

311
00:31:30.720 --> 00:31:32.199
Triple eight!

312
00:31:32.320 --> 00:31:34.914
Nine points for me.

313
00:31:35.560 --> 00:31:38.074
What's happening with the cards?

314
00:31:38.200 --> 00:31:41.351
- She's on a hot streak.
- She just got lucky.

315
00:31:41.480 --> 00:31:44.950
Just got lucky. that's all. boss.

316
00:31:45.080 --> 00:31:47.310
I got a nine!

317
00:31:48.960 --> 00:31:52.077
- Eight points again!
- Nine points again!

318
00:31:52.200 --> 00:31:53.349
Fuck!

319
00:31:53.480 --> 00:31:56.119
I win again! Pay up!

320
00:31:58.480 --> 00:32:00.436
Double eight for me!

321
00:32:01.360 --> 00:32:03.669
You lose. Pay up.

322
00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:08.629
- Double eight for me again!
- Double nine for me again!

323
00:32:10.200 --> 00:32:12.760
Everybody. leave your cards on the table.

324
00:32:13.680 --> 00:32:16.672
I want to see if this chick's cheating.

325
00:32:16.800 --> 00:32:20.270
She's got nine points 15 times.
and I lost every round.

326
00:32:20.400 --> 00:32:24.029
She's cleaned you out.
You understand?

327
00:32:24.720 --> 00:32:27.029
Let's prove it this time.

328
00:32:27.160 --> 00:32:31.517
If you get a nine this time.
you're definitely cheating. you bitch!

329
00:32:32.200 --> 00:32:34.316
Let's see...

330
00:32:34.440 --> 00:32:37.477
I've got clear eight again!

331
00:32:37.600 --> 00:32:41.195
If you get nine points.
you'd better watch out!

332
00:32:43.760 --> 00:32:45.990
You see. boss. she got four points.

333
00:32:46.120 --> 00:32:47.519
Look!

334
00:32:47.640 --> 00:32:49.437
I don't believe it.

335
00:32:49.560 --> 00:32:51.391
She has hidden cards.

336
00:32:51.520 --> 00:32:54.592
- I'll search her.
- Calm down. I'll handle it.

337
00:32:54.720 --> 00:32:56.199
Frisk her. George.

338
00:32:56.320 --> 00:32:59.312
- Are you hiding cards?
- Absolutely not.

339
00:32:59.440 --> 00:33:01.795
- Let's see.
- Where?

340
00:33:01.920 --> 00:33:03.194
In the pockets?

341
00:33:03.320 --> 00:33:05.197
- Let me find them.
- It's OK.

342
00:33:05.320 --> 00:33:07.072
C'mon. get lost! Go!

343
00:33:07.200 --> 00:33:10.829
- No! Frisk her all over.
- I have. Go on. scram!

344
00:33:10.960 --> 00:33:14.714
Bugger off!
Don't let me see you again! Bitch!

345
00:33:14.840 --> 00:33:18.116
You bring bad luck. See. he lost.
Let's get back to it.

346
00:33:18.240 --> 00:33:21.789
- Let's fleece these suckers.
- There's nobody left to fleece!

347
00:33:21.920 --> 00:33:25.071
- She cleaned them out.
- Don't blame me.

348
00:33:25.200 --> 00:33:28.636
We've got 8.000 baht in all.
3.000 baht for you. for college fees...

349
00:33:28.760 --> 00:33:32.389
- What? Only 3.000?
- You don't need any more.

350
00:33:32.520 --> 00:33:37.071
- Why's that all I get?
- Take it and don't spend it all.

351
00:33:37.200 --> 00:33:39.839
- Give me another 1.000.
- No! 3.000's fine.

352
00:33:39.960 --> 00:33:42.030
It's not enough to cover my college fees.

353
00:33:43.720 --> 00:33:44.994
Filthy rich!

354
00:33:45.600 --> 00:33:49.070
Not that shithead again.
Give me that.

355
00:33:49.200 --> 00:33:52.795
- It's mine!
- It's a loan. Don't worry!

356
00:33:53.400 --> 00:33:57.916
What a coincidence!
I was on my way over. Here's the money.

357
00:33:58.040 --> 00:34:00.235
- Hey. that's mine!
- What?

358
00:34:02.440 --> 00:34:05.079
There's 8.000.
The rest later.

359
00:34:05.200 --> 00:34:07.919
Don't look so pissed off.

360
00:34:08.040 --> 00:34:12.716
Screw the rest of the money.
You two ripped me off.

361
00:34:12.840 --> 00:34:14.273
I hate that.

362
00:34:17.320 --> 00:34:19.311
I can't fight all of you!

363
00:34:21.800 --> 00:34:23.358
Ting!

364
00:34:26.920 --> 00:34:28.797
I'm not fighting.

365
00:34:32.320 --> 00:34:34.038
Rip me off. would you?

366
00:34:37.480 --> 00:34:39.311
Who the fuck are you?

367
00:34:46.360 --> 00:34:48.271
Stay out of this. dipshit!

368
00:34:58.720 --> 00:35:00.676
I'll get you for this!

369
00:35:04.000 --> 00:35:06.309
I owe you one. Ting.

370
00:35:06.440 --> 00:35:08.908
I'll take you to find Ong-Bak.

371
00:35:11.080 --> 00:35:14.072
Will you fight for me just once more?

372
00:35:15.120 --> 00:35:17.350
Wait! Listen to me!

373
00:35:17.480 --> 00:35:22.190
You saw the trouble I was in.
If I don't pay up. I'm dead.

374
00:35:22.320 --> 00:35:25.630
Help me. Fight once more.
Last time. Please...

375
00:35:25.760 --> 00:35:26.715
Lay off him.

376
00:35:26.840 --> 00:35:32.233
So don't help me! Dimwit! Shithead!
Screw your stupid village.

377
00:35:32.360 --> 00:35:35.955
Sending one guy against
a Burmese gang to recover Ong-Bak?

378
00:35:36.080 --> 00:35:37.354
Crazy!

379
00:35:37.480 --> 00:35:40.074
If Ong-Bak's so great.
why's he headless?

380
00:35:40.200 --> 00:35:42.191
Just a bit of rock!

381
00:35:45.360 --> 00:35:47.749
Why did you hit me?

382
00:35:47.880 --> 00:35:50.872
- You're cousins. cut it out!
- He hit me!

383
00:35:51.000 --> 00:35:53.878
Forget it.
Look who's come for you!

384
00:35:55.760 --> 00:35:57.478
Peng!

385
00:35:57.600 --> 00:36:02.594
One beating not enough?
You're a glutton for punishment.

386
00:36:05.080 --> 00:36:07.150
I get the picture.

387
00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:14.195
Listen. George.
You know what you have to do. right?

388
00:36:14.880 --> 00:36:18.793
Muay. you know what you have to do.

389
00:36:20.240 --> 00:36:22.196
Fend for yourself!

390
00:36:25.440 --> 00:36:28.000
Hey. wait for me!

391
00:36:29.120 --> 00:36:31.270
Get them!

392
00:36:43.160 --> 00:36:45.628
Follow him.
The rest with me.

393
00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:56.515
You!

394
00:36:56.640 --> 00:36:58.153
I'm outta here!

395
00:37:23.120 --> 00:37:25.350
Hey. out of my way!

396
00:37:37.840 --> 00:37:39.796
How does he do that?

397
00:37:45.440 --> 00:37:48.477
My ass! How did I do that?

398
00:38:22.760 --> 00:38:25.035
Definitely not my lucky day!

399
00:38:36.720 --> 00:38:38.517
Lend me your knife.

400
00:38:38.640 --> 00:38:41.359
Come on!
I'll skin you alive! Wanker!

401
00:38:55.800 --> 00:39:03.036
Knives... Knives...
Knives for sale!

402
00:39:36.200 --> 00:39:37.076
CRUSHED CHILLIS

403
00:39:41.120 --> 00:39:41.916
CURRY PASTE

404
00:39:59.720 --> 00:40:02.473
Catch them and kill them!

405
00:41:27.320 --> 00:41:29.709
Ting! Help me!

406
00:41:29.840 --> 00:41:32.149
No! You're scum. just like Don.

407
00:41:32.640 --> 00:41:36.155
I know where to find him.
I'll take you there.

408
00:41:36.280 --> 00:41:38.396
I know his hangouts.

409
00:42:07.960 --> 00:42:10.474
I've seen Don selling drugs here.

410
00:42:10.600 --> 00:42:13.239
If you don't believe me. ask Muay.

411
00:42:14.320 --> 00:42:15.992
Anyway. today...

412
00:42:16.720 --> 00:42:18.790
Shit! Where...

413
00:42:25.200 --> 00:42:27.430
He's here. boss.

414
00:42:32.840 --> 00:42:37.914
If I arrange for the boxer
to fight Big Bear. are you in?

415
00:42:38.840 --> 00:42:42.469
Could be.
What are the stakes?

416
00:43:02.120 --> 00:43:06.238
Welcome to the champion.
Ting the Pradu Legend!

417
00:43:22.120 --> 00:43:25.829
- What's going on?
- Big Bear's goading Ting.

418
00:43:59.840 --> 00:44:02.434
Come on. I'll fight with you.

419
00:44:02.560 --> 00:44:05.279
I'll teach you Muay Thai. Come on!

420
00:44:11.120 --> 00:44:12.951
Come on!

421
00:44:31.960 --> 00:44:34.394
- Have you seen Don?
- No.

422
00:44:34.520 --> 00:44:38.354
But I see a Thai getting beaten up.
You're a coward.

423
00:44:48.400 --> 00:44:52.109
You just going to watch?
If you don't help him. he's dead.

424
00:44:56.520 --> 00:44:58.397
Ting!

425
00:45:02.600 --> 00:45:06.229
What kind of a person are you!
Help him or I won't help you find Ong-Bak.

426
00:45:06.360 --> 00:45:11.036
You can discuss it later.
but that guy needs help now!

427
00:45:49.640 --> 00:45:53.155
Come on! Five to one!
Come on! Five to one!

428
00:45:53.280 --> 00:45:56.192
Come on! Five to one!
Come on! Five to one!

429
00:45:56.320 --> 00:45:59.153
I'll give you two to one.
What do you think?

430
00:45:59.800 --> 00:46:01.916
OK. I bet three million.

431
00:46:13.440 --> 00:46:15.078
Batha Loop Pak. (Great Kick.)

432
00:46:26.240 --> 00:46:28.629
Hanuman Kham Loka.
(Great Monkey Crossing World.)

433
00:46:32.520 --> 00:46:35.478
If he wins. give me the prize money.

434
00:46:35.600 --> 00:46:38.558
- Yes! I know that!
- Thanks. brother.

435
00:47:20.240 --> 00:47:22.435
Way to go! You're the best!

436
00:47:23.760 --> 00:47:26.593
Looks like you can't
get your capital back today.

437
00:48:11.040 --> 00:48:18.071
The next fight. Ting the Pradu Legend
and Toshiro!

438
00:48:45.040 --> 00:48:48.077
Well done!
Muay. where's the moneybag?

439
00:48:48.200 --> 00:48:51.795
- What for?
- I'll only bet half of it.

440
00:48:51.920 --> 00:48:53.353
- Sure?
- Trust me!

441
00:48:53.480 --> 00:48:54.799
- Don't take the lot.
- Sure.

442
00:50:34.280 --> 00:50:36.999
Another challenger?
This time. no odds.

443
00:50:38.160 --> 00:50:40.720
Sure. Ten million on the table.

444
00:50:40.840 --> 00:50:42.956
No problem!

445
00:53:05.640 --> 00:53:07.915
Leave me alone!
Let go of me!

446
00:53:08.040 --> 00:53:10.793
Help! Help me!

447
00:53:14.120 --> 00:53:16.680
Let go of me!
Why are you holding me?

448
00:54:24.280 --> 00:54:26.157
You're the best. Ting!

449
00:54:26.280 --> 00:54:29.829
I told you. Muay. we should have bet it all.
We'd be filthy rich!

450
00:54:29.960 --> 00:54:33.589
Surprised. aren't you?
You stupid fuck! I'm fucking rich!

451
00:55:25.760 --> 00:55:28.035
Muay. pick it up.

452
00:55:28.160 --> 00:55:31.596
Let's call it a day.
You won't get your share back.

453
00:55:34.000 --> 00:55:35.752
Pulped.

454
00:55:37.160 --> 00:55:41.472
Ting. at this rate
we're going to make a fortune.

455
00:55:41.600 --> 00:55:42.919
Fantastic!

456
00:55:43.840 --> 00:55:45.034
Don!

457
00:55:48.000 --> 00:55:50.355
The police have just arrived!

458
00:55:52.400 --> 00:55:54.391
Follow them!

459
00:55:55.400 --> 00:55:56.674
Out of the way!

460
00:55:56.800 --> 00:55:58.791
C'mon. get in!

461
00:56:08.200 --> 00:56:09.394
Wait! Stop!

462
00:56:10.920 --> 00:56:15.391
I have to deliver this week.
Tell your guys to box up the goods.

463
00:56:15.520 --> 00:56:17.431
And no fuck-ups. OK?

464
00:56:17.560 --> 00:56:19.039
Yes. boss.

465
00:56:20.000 --> 00:56:21.956
How do you know the hick?

466
00:56:23.800 --> 00:56:27.759
Humlae. how are we going to find Don?

467
00:56:27.880 --> 00:56:29.996
Eat first. Eat!

468
00:56:30.120 --> 00:56:32.714
Don't worry. We'll find him.

469
00:56:32.840 --> 00:56:36.389
Around here. everybody knows him.
Eat up!

470
00:56:36.960 --> 00:56:40.111
Muay. come with me tomorrow.

471
00:56:40.240 --> 00:56:43.152
We may have a way
to make some cash to spend.

472
00:56:43.280 --> 00:56:45.157
No way.
I have an exam tomorrow.

473
00:56:45.280 --> 00:56:47.874
Exam?
Stupid bitch. you never go to college.

474
00:56:48.000 --> 00:56:50.992
How could you pass!
Are you screwing your teacher?

475
00:56:51.120 --> 00:56:54.396
- Come again?
- Just kidding. a little joke.

476
00:56:54.520 --> 00:56:57.637
You're a good student.
Great student. Eat! Eat up!

477
00:57:02.200 --> 00:57:04.555
Thanks for agreeing to help
bring back Ong-Bak.

478
00:57:04.680 --> 00:57:06.796
- It's OK.
- Your dad will be pleased.

479
00:57:06.920 --> 00:57:12.074
George. you owe me three months' rent.
What's your excuse?

480
00:57:12.200 --> 00:57:17.228
Give me another three days. OK?
I'll have your money then. Definitely.

481
00:57:17.360 --> 00:57:22.195
You always say that.
I want it today or you're out!

482
00:57:22.960 --> 00:57:25.428
- Take this ring instead.
- OK. then.

483
00:57:26.240 --> 00:57:28.959
You have another week to pay up.

484
00:57:29.760 --> 00:57:34.595
If you don't. you clear out
of my apartment. Get it?

485
00:58:03.960 --> 00:58:06.758
"I want you to come home with Ting."

486
00:58:06.880 --> 00:58:09.599
"Don't worry about bringing back money."

487
00:58:09.720 --> 00:58:13.633
"Or about getting ordained.
Don't worry. I don't mind."

488
00:58:13.760 --> 00:58:17.753
"Just come and visit us.
I'm thinking of you."

489
00:59:06.120 --> 00:59:09.351
Why not?
I'm not as good as your ex?

490
00:59:10.000 --> 00:59:11.718
Shit!

491
00:59:13.720 --> 00:59:15.676
Fucking spoilt my mood!

492
00:59:18.640 --> 00:59:20.358
Don...

493
00:59:21.040 --> 00:59:23.952
I won't push your drugs any more.

494
00:59:25.720 --> 00:59:27.358
Why not?

495
00:59:34.960 --> 00:59:37.155
I want to kick it.

496
00:59:43.800 --> 00:59:45.836
You want to kick it?

497
00:59:48.560 --> 00:59:51.597
You want to clean up?
Here!

498
00:59:53.880 --> 00:59:56.633
Think you can quit just like that?

499
00:59:56.760 --> 01:00:00.992
If you think you can. go ahead.
Go right ahead!

500
01:00:25.680 --> 01:00:27.716
Who the fuck...?

501
01:00:37.200 --> 01:00:39.270
- Ting!
- Don't run away!

502
01:00:40.160 --> 01:00:41.593
Ting!

503
01:00:42.360 --> 01:00:43.759
You!

504
01:00:46.640 --> 01:00:48.278
Ngek! Ngek!

505
01:00:50.520 --> 01:00:52.829
- Where's Ong-Bak?
- I don't know.

506
01:00:52.960 --> 01:00:56.350
- You took it.
- I said I don't know.

507
01:00:56.480 --> 01:00:57.913
Ting!

508
01:00:58.480 --> 01:01:00.072
Go! Go!

509
01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:05.069
Ngek!

510
01:01:14.720 --> 01:01:17.837
- What's happened. Don?
- Get that guy! Go!

511
01:01:24.320 --> 01:01:27.198
Call an ambulance now.
Room 212. someone's dying!

512
01:01:39.320 --> 01:01:41.709
Ting. come on! Get in.

513
01:01:47.080 --> 01:01:48.433
You're fucking dead!

514
01:02:46.000 --> 01:02:47.752
Christ! Why do you keep following me?

515
01:03:07.040 --> 01:03:09.076
- Brake!
- Die!

516
01:03:20.720 --> 01:03:21.869
Ting!

517
01:03:24.600 --> 01:03:25.874
Ting!

518
01:03:28.160 --> 01:03:31.436
Ting. brake! Brake! Quick!

519
01:03:51.920 --> 01:03:53.114
Get them! Go!

520
01:06:23.200 --> 01:06:27.512
Make sure you check everything's OK.
No mistakes.

521
01:06:27.640 --> 01:06:31.553
Most importantly. don't let in
anyone you don't know! Get it?

522
01:06:32.280 --> 01:06:34.714
The fucker never gives up!
Get in!

523
01:08:33.840 --> 01:08:35.796
Get in.

524
01:08:38.840 --> 01:08:43.391
The police and the Heritage Department
have recovered many stolen antiques

525
01:08:43.520 --> 01:08:46.432
hidden at this Chao Praya fish farm.

526
01:08:46.560 --> 01:08:49.199
The hoard is said to be priceless.

527
01:08:49.320 --> 01:08:52.790
Each piece is a national treasure...

528
01:08:53.160 --> 01:08:56.470
The Heritage Department
will be in charge.

529
01:08:56.600 --> 01:09:00.275
registering them as national treasures.

530
01:09:14.200 --> 01:09:17.954
I told you to stay out of trouble.
Not to stick your nose in.

531
01:09:18.080 --> 01:09:21.356
I didn't start it.
They were looking for Ong-Bak.

532
01:09:23.120 --> 01:09:24.758
What is Ong-Bak?

533
01:09:25.920 --> 01:09:28.798
You know. the Buddha's head
I brought you.

534
01:09:28.920 --> 01:09:31.559
Shithead! Why did they want
to harass me?

535
01:09:32.200 --> 01:09:33.838
I lost a ten-million bet

536
01:09:33.960 --> 01:09:38.431
and now you screw up my business
with some Buddha's head!

537
01:09:41.520 --> 01:09:43.590
BAMRUNGRAT HOSPITAL

538
01:09:48.640 --> 01:09:52.758
I'm sorry. we couldn't save her.

539
01:09:56.080 --> 01:09:59.993
Ngek... Ngek... Big sister!

540
01:10:00.120 --> 01:10:01.997
Big sister!

541
01:10:02.120 --> 01:10:05.157
Don't leave me!

542
01:10:05.720 --> 01:10:09.315
- Who is she?
- Muay's sister.

543
01:10:09.440 --> 01:10:13.991
Who's going to live with me?

544
01:10:15.480 --> 01:10:20.076
Who's going to live with me?

545
01:10:20.200 --> 01:10:21.519
Muay.

546
01:10:22.240 --> 01:10:24.037
Muay.

547
01:10:25.480 --> 01:10:29.519
Take this. Ngek gave this to you.

548
01:10:32.160 --> 01:10:34.549
"Muay's term fees."

549
01:10:34.680 --> 01:10:38.798
I don't want it! I don't want anything!
I told you I didn't want it!

550
01:10:38.920 --> 01:10:43.277
I don't want anything!
You have to stay with me!

551
01:10:43.400 --> 01:10:47.757
Why did it have to happen like this?
Stay with me!

552
01:10:48.080 --> 01:10:53.029
Don't be so sad. Muay.
Everyone has to die some day.

553
01:10:53.920 --> 01:10:55.751
I'll be here for you.

554
01:10:56.280 --> 01:10:58.157
What the...?

555
01:10:58.280 --> 01:11:01.477
- Where are you taking us? I'm not going.
- Go! Quick!

556
01:11:03.200 --> 01:11:05.111
Go! Go! Go!

557
01:11:14.600 --> 01:11:18.479
You don't know
who you're messing with!

558
01:11:19.360 --> 01:11:22.397
Uh... I know... nothing about it.

559
01:11:22.520 --> 01:11:24.954
It's between Ting and Don.
Honest!

560
01:11:25.080 --> 01:11:27.310
I don't know anything.

561
01:11:39.840 --> 01:11:44.356
I know... you're looking for this head.

562
01:11:45.840 --> 01:11:47.876
You're very persistent.

563
01:11:50.480 --> 01:11:54.234
If you want.
I have a game we can play.

564
01:12:01.040 --> 01:12:04.032
I saw Ong-Bak with my own eyes.

565
01:12:04.160 --> 01:12:07.869
Just one rope fist fight
and he'll give him back.

566
01:12:08.000 --> 01:12:10.594
And he'll release Muay.

567
01:12:10.720 --> 01:12:14.508
What do you say?
What are you going to do?

568
01:12:17.600 --> 01:12:23.436
I'll do anything you ask
to take Ong-Bak home to our village.

569
01:12:25.480 --> 01:12:28.438
Even if it means it'll cost me my life.

570
01:12:29.760 --> 01:12:32.399
BO XING HALL
THAI - MYANMAR BORDER

571
01:12:46.280 --> 01:12:49.511
Why hold this fight on the border?

572
01:12:51.080 --> 01:12:53.230
Just a change of scenery.

573
01:12:53.360 --> 01:12:55.396
I wanted a rope fist fight.

574
01:12:55.520 --> 01:12:59.149
Out here. if anyone dies.
it won't be a problem.

575
01:12:59.480 --> 01:13:03.393
You hate the country boy so much
you want him dead?

576
01:13:04.240 --> 01:13:07.676
If you're feeling lucky.
name the stakes.

577
01:13:08.520 --> 01:13:10.715
You're sounding like a loser.

578
01:14:03.160 --> 01:14:05.230
And now for the main event.

579
01:14:05.360 --> 01:14:07.669
In the eastern corner.
Ting the Pradu Legend.

580
01:14:07.800 --> 01:14:12.635
Ting is an up-and-coming fighter.
one to watch.

581
01:14:12.760 --> 01:14:16.514
In the western corner.
a Burmese boxer: Sa-Ming Sibtid.

582
01:14:16.640 --> 01:14:19.108
out to prove his country's worth.

583
01:14:19.240 --> 01:14:21.800
The stage is set.
Bring it on. guys!

584
01:14:21.920 --> 01:14:27.870
For Sa-Ming Sibtid. this is his first bout
after a long absence. He may be rusty.

585
01:14:28.000 --> 01:14:31.390
Sa-Ming fixes Ting with a stare.

586
01:14:31.920 --> 01:14:35.754
Ting kicks with the left.
Then right. then left again.

587
01:14:35.880 --> 01:14:38.952
Misses with a roundhouse.
It's gonna be a very exciting match.

588
01:14:39.080 --> 01:14:41.036
Both of them look up for it.

589
01:16:10.800 --> 01:16:12.631
Ting! Ting!

590
01:16:54.640 --> 01:16:58.519
Hey. if you want Ong-Bak.
come with me.

591
01:17:27.440 --> 01:17:32.389
Your reward for getting country boy
to throw the fight.

592
01:17:41.880 --> 01:17:43.677
Hey. respect the Buddha image!

593
01:17:43.800 --> 01:17:48.794
I don't revere lumps of stone
like you. the country folks.

594
01:17:48.920 --> 01:17:51.639
I have no faith in religion.

595
01:17:51.760 --> 01:17:54.399
I only believe in myself.

596
01:17:54.520 --> 01:17:56.715
You must respect me.

597
01:17:56.840 --> 01:18:00.150
I am God.
I decide if you live or die.

598
01:18:01.880 --> 01:18:04.758
Bastard! You double-crossed us!

599
01:18:05.560 --> 01:18:09.075
You wanted Ting to lose and he threw
the fight. Now hand over Ong-Bak.

600
01:18:09.200 --> 01:18:11.430
Motherfucker!
You promised me!

601
01:18:16.240 --> 01:18:21.109
That shit hunk of rock
cost me 100 million baht.

602
01:18:22.120 --> 01:18:25.874
Don't think
I'll ever give it back to him.

603
01:18:26.000 --> 01:18:30.039
Remember. I am God.

604
01:18:30.160 --> 01:18:33.835
Dispose of them
and meet me at the cave.

605
01:18:49.120 --> 01:18:51.395
Kill them.

606
01:19:03.040 --> 01:19:04.439
George!

607
01:19:05.880 --> 01:19:08.394
Shithead! I told you to be discreet.

608
01:19:23.000 --> 01:19:26.151
Hey! Quick!
You'll have the cops after us!

609
01:19:34.880 --> 01:19:37.110
There! Get them!

610
01:21:27.320 --> 01:21:29.629
Where's Ong-Bak?

611
01:21:31.000 --> 01:21:33.833
Cave in E-Keng mountain...

612
01:21:45.080 --> 01:21:47.958
- Hey. let me come with you.
- No.

613
01:21:48.640 --> 01:21:51.200
I won't let anyone die for Ong-Bak.

614
01:21:51.320 --> 01:21:54.437
If someone must. it will be me.

615
01:21:54.560 --> 01:21:56.437
Damn you.

616
01:21:59.360 --> 01:22:02.432
Ting... Ting...

617
01:22:04.960 --> 01:22:06.951
Let me help you.

618
01:22:09.160 --> 01:22:12.596
I never wanted it to turn out this way.

619
01:22:12.720 --> 01:22:17.350
Forgive me. Let me do something
for Nong Pradu. Just once!

620
01:22:18.760 --> 01:22:22.036
Let me start the bike for you. at least.

621
01:22:25.000 --> 01:22:28.356
I'm Humlae of Nong Pradu village.

622
01:22:40.760 --> 01:22:45.436
Don said that round the other side
of E-Keng mountain there's a cave.

623
01:26:25.640 --> 01:26:28.438
You never give up. do you?

624
01:26:34.680 --> 01:26:38.912
If you put your life on the line
for this tiny head.

625
01:26:39.040 --> 01:26:41.190
what about this one?

626
01:29:35.760 --> 01:29:38.274
Humlae. are you OK?

627
01:29:44.840 --> 01:29:48.310
Go and rescue Ong-Bak.
Hurry!

628
01:29:50.520 --> 01:29:53.830
Don't worry about me.
Get Ong-Bak. Now!

629
01:30:57.360 --> 01:31:00.193
Hey. where are they running off to?

630
01:31:00.320 --> 01:31:04.108
Carry on working on it.
Get the head.

631
01:31:11.080 --> 01:31:12.274
Hey.

632
01:31:12.400 --> 01:31:13.992
Be careful.

633
01:31:14.120 --> 01:31:16.509
Don't let him win.

634
01:32:25.560 --> 01:32:27.391
Ready. boss.

635
01:32:27.520 --> 01:32:30.512
Good. Hoist it up.

636
01:36:11.880 --> 01:36:13.916
You want it?

637
01:36:14.040 --> 01:36:16.679
What if I smash it to pieces?

638
01:36:16.800 --> 01:36:18.711
You like it. don't you?

639
01:36:18.840 --> 01:36:19.955
Don't!

640
01:37:38.480 --> 01:37:40.198
Humlae!

641
01:37:41.520 --> 01:37:44.159
Humlae. are you OK?

642
01:37:48.480 --> 01:37:54.271
Get hold of Ong-Bak...
and take him home.

643
01:37:55.640 --> 01:37:56.959
George!

644
01:37:57.080 --> 01:37:59.389
Why did it turn out like this?

645
01:38:01.120 --> 01:38:02.792
- Can you hear me?
- Humlae!

646
01:38:02.920 --> 01:38:04.399
Muay...

647
01:38:05.320 --> 01:38:11.555
Study hard. get... the degree...

648
01:38:12.720 --> 01:38:15.473
and find a good job.

649
01:38:21.640 --> 01:38:26.430
Ting. tell my father...

650
01:38:26.920 --> 01:38:33.109
I'm sorry. I won't be... ordained.

651
01:38:33.240 --> 01:38:38.234
Why d'you say that?
We'll get you to the hospital. You'll be OK.

652
01:38:38.360 --> 01:38:39.713
Humlae!

653
01:38:39.840 --> 01:38:42.070
George! George!

654
01:38:44.240 --> 01:38:46.196
You can't die!

655
01:38:46.320 --> 01:38:49.790
You promised to take care of me!
You can't die!

656
01:38:49.920 --> 01:38:53.390
Don't do this to me!
Don't fucking lie to me!

657
01:38:53.520 --> 01:38:57.991
Don't lie! Don't fucking lie!
You promised me!

658
01:38:58.120 --> 01:39:00.998
I don't have anybody.
No one's left.

659
01:39:01.120 --> 01:39:06.274
Wake up now!
Why are you fucking doing this to me?

660
01:39:06.400 --> 01:39:09.472
Don't do this to me!

661
01:39:09.600 --> 01:39:11.511
George. you can't die!

662
01:39:11.640 --> 01:39:14.234
Don't die!
